WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.595
Agar bizda Emi ismli turtle bo‘lsa,

00:00:02.595 --> 00:00:09.569
keyin Emi.forward (50) bayonoti turtle ni 50 pikselga oldinga siljishiga olib keladi.

00:00:09.569 --> 00:00:16.625
Xuddi shunday, Emi.back (50) turtle ning 50 pikselga orqaga siljishiga olib keladi.

00:00:16.625 --> 00:00:19.500
Yozayotganda tushunish kerak bo‘lgan bir narsa

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:24.555
turtle dasturlari shundaki, yo‘nalishlar barchasi turtle lar nuqtai nazaridan hisoblanadi.

00:00:24.555 --> 00:00:26.550
Bu biroz chalkash bo‘lishi mumkin

00:00:26.550 --> 00:00:29.985
avval turtle chapga yoki o‘ngga burilishini aytganda.

00:00:29.985 --> 00:00:32.724
Dasturning istalgan nuqtasida,

00:00:32.724 --> 00:00:36.335
turtle ma’lum bir yo‘nalishga qaragan.

00:00:36.335 --> 00:00:39.625
turtle 45 ga chapga burilishini aytganda,

00:00:39.625 --> 00:00:45.700
Siz uni hozir qarayotgan tarafdan 45 gradusga burishingiz kerakligini aytmoqdasiz.

00:00:45.700 --> 00:00:49.195
Shunday qilib, agar biz turtle kvadrat chizmoqchi bo‘lsak,

00:00:49.195 --> 00:00:52.760
biz 100 pikselga oldinga siljishi kerakligini aytishimiz kerak,

00:00:52.760 --> 00:00:56.740
keyin 90 gradusga chapga burilib,

00:00:56.740 --> 00:00:59.695
oldinga 100, chap 90,

00:00:59.695 --> 00:01:04.105
oldinga 100, chap 90, oldinga 100,

00:01:04.105 --> 00:01:09.840
va endi u boshqa tomonga qaragan bo‘lsa-da, boshlagan jo‘yiga qaytdi.

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:12.920
Ba’zida bu biroz chalkash tuyulishi mumkin.

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:16.845
Masalan, agar siz shunga o‘xshash uchburchak chizmoqchi bo‘lsangiz,

00:01:16.845 --> 00:01:20.350
turtle ni burib qo‘yishni o‘ylayotgandirsiz

00:01:20.350 --> 00:01:24.375
60 gradusga teng bo‘lgan uchburchak ichidagi burchaklarga.

00:01:24.375 --> 00:01:31.370
Aslida, siz turtle ni 120 daraja burchaklar bilan burishingizni xohlaysiz.

00:01:31.370 --> 00:01:35.950
Albatta, siz adashib qolsangiz yoki unchalik ishonchingiz komil bo‘lmasa,

00:01:35.950 --> 00:01:37.764
har doim tajriba o‘tkazishingiz mumkin.

00:01:37.764 --> 00:01:42.120
Qanday natijalarga erishishingizni ko‘rish uchun turli xil burchaklarni sinab ko‘rishdan qo‘rqmang.

